      • endpointHandler

        public AnswerResponseBody endpointHandler(java.lang.String payload,
                                          Players players,
                                          FullQuestions questions)
        Endpoint handler.

        If the payload is valid JSON, then the persistence objects and payload begin the first level of the Dungeon of Sorrows... aka - the three levels of determinition logic that was too confusing to fit into one method.

        Each level performs an input validation check and, if that check passes, passes everything to the next level.

        Parameters:
        payload - the payload
        players - the players
        questions - the questions
        Returns:
        the answer response body
